<title>Mental Health Key Messages</title>
<description>As China's interpersonal competition becomes more and more severe. Many students and researchers commit suicide. Here I present some useful resources for my own purposes:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Key Messages:&lt;br&gt;Well done! You're taking proactive steps to prioritize your mental well-being. &lt;br&gt;Reaching out for support shows real courage and resilience. &lt;br&gt;Remember, your mental health is important, and you don't have to go through this alone. &lt;br&gt;Feel free to utilize the various supports available, including professional services. &lt;br&gt;You've got this! Keep making your mental health a top priority.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
