<title>Thoughts on Debian Pure Blend</title>
<description>Debian Pure Blend provides an amazing amount of FOSS professional tools in almost every discipline.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can do scientific research, process GIS data, play with medical image processing tools and listen to hamradio. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This research used to depend on large laboratory and an enormous mount of money. But now is available to all human beings, free and opensource. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
